{
  "stem": "3928.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I still believe in, today, this, that's my dead mother looking out for me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And apparently, she did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Then, I was taken to the hospital and checked out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I was nothing wrong with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I went, and I checked with the people, you know, whom were in hiding.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Then, I had to go and pick up more people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the Russians came closer and closer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I had to go up and work with Otto Skorzeny.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Otto Skorzeny, he was in charge SS, like he was something like a SS brigadier general, you know, with--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His big thing was, he was driving a BMW 1,000, you know, with the side-car and a bazooka mounted this.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was his-- his big thing, you know, this?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He-- he's invincible, you know, he felt, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he wanted to work with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He wanted me to go with him to Germany, you know, and to be a liaison between the Hungarian army, who were, at the time, since the Russians came closer and closer, they go-- they went to Austria, with them, you know, to go with them.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I told him, sure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I will do it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Naturally, I wouldn't say no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and then, in-- we had to get food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I just went all kinds of places, you know, in German uniform.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I just took whatever was there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I went to restaurants, back room and everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I had my machine gun with me, I think.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's for the German army.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's for the German army.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, when I went to the German army where they feed us, you know, in Ludovica Academy, I just took everything for the headquarters there, when I can get a hold to help my aunt feed the people.",
      "word_count": 39
    }
  ],
